reviewText:
Was hoping for so much more.
Too few players included with way too few highlights.
It's also put together like any amateur could've done it.

this video is pretty basic.  only issue i have is the years they showed were the best years ever and they only had about 3 of the same highlights for each player.  there were tons and tons of highlights they could have used.  anyway good product and will be looked at for years to come
